# ── Compiled artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Bundles compile to /tmp (just run NAME == c++ ... -o /tmp/cpp_NAME && /tmp/cpp_NAME),
# so NOTHING lands in the source dir. This guards against accidental in-source builds.
*.o
*.out
cpp_*
*.exe

# ── Phase 8 CMake build dirs (per-developer) ────────────────────────────────
build/
cmake-build-*/
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
!Justfile

# ── Coverage / profiling (Phase 7 sanitizers + Phase 8 benchmarking) ────────
*.profraw
*.profdata
gcov/
*.gcda
*.gcno
callgrind.out.*
vgcore.*

# ── Package-manager caches (vcpkg/Conan — Phase 8 / walkthroughs) ──────────
.vcpkg-root
vcpkg_installed/
.build/

# ── Editor / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Local env / secrets (NEVER commit) ──────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
*.local

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DO NOT IGNORE (these ARE committed — they are the bundle, not artifacts):
#   *_output.txt      captured stdout (== go/*_output.txt, rust/*_output.txt)
#                     — ground truth, the .md pastes it verbatim
#   CMakeLists.txt    only if/when a Phase 8 / walkthrough adds one
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
